  <!-- EN: These colonists participated in the victory for the quest [resolvedQuestName]. [asker_definite] wants to know who should receive the [royalFavorReward_amount] [asker_faction_royalFavorLabel] for this service. -->
  <VFEM2_OpportunitySite_Skirmish.root.nodes.15.node.nodes.1.nodeIfChosenPawnSignalUsed.text>Эти поселенцы приняли участие в успешном завершении задания [resolvedQuestName]. [asker_definite] спрашивает, кому из них за свою службу причитается [royalFavorReward_amount] ед. {lookup: [asker_faction_royalFavorLabel]; Case; 1}.</VFEM2_OpportunitySite_Skirmish.root.nodes.15.node.nodes.1.nodeIfChosenPawnSignalUsed.text>
